Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,would just say, you know, if I have a\Ndisorder, I'd say, is this Raike
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.52,0:18:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,therapist over 200? Yeah. U this is\Nhelpful to my Raiki is going to be
