Dialogue: 0,1:32:47.36,1:32:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,program? I don't really do I do do I\Nreally want to do radio programs?
Dialogue: 0,1:32:53.92,1:32:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well,\Nto have this kind of knowledge and not
Dialogue: 0,1:32:57.67,1:33:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,share it with others.\NIn other words, to have certain
Dialogue: 0,1:33:03.84,1:33:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,knowledge that could be helpful to\Nothers, one gets joy out of sharing it
Dialogue: 0,1:33:08.32,1:33:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,for whatever. See, it would be like Sir\NAlex Fleming, you know, discovered
