Dialogue: 0,1:34:04.48,1:34:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,engagements, talk to everybody that you\Ncould all day long, but you have rent to
Dialogue: 0,1:34:08.88,1:34:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,pay. So I look at it if something pays\Nthe rent and frees your time so that you
Dialogue: 0,1:34:14.15,1:34:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,can spend that time teaching, then\Nyou're giving it back to the world. You
